#: admin/templates/wpc-receiving-submenu.tpl.php:63
#: templates/single-barcode.tpl.php:45
msgid ""
"Scan your shipment barcode to update or enter the tracking number and press "
"ENTER"
msgstr ""
"Pindai kode batang pengiriman Anda untuk memperbarui atau memasukkan nomor "
"pelacakan dan tekan ENTER"

#: admin/templates/wpc-receiving-submenu.tpl.php:81
#: templates/single-barcode.tpl.php:53
msgid "Notes:"
msgstr "Catatan:"

#: admin/templates/wpc-receiving-submenu.tpl.php:83
msgid ""
"If you have connected your barcode scanner please scan directly to the "
"barcode and it will automatic update the Shipment Status"
msgstr ""
"Jika Anda telah menghubungkan pemindai kode batang Anda, silakan pindai "
"langsung ke kode batang dan itu akan secara otomatis memperbarui Status "
"Pengiriman"

#: admin/templates/wpc-receiving-submenu.tpl.php:84
msgid ""
"If you don't have a barcode scanner please input it to the tracking number "
"field and press <i>Enter</i> on your keyboard"
msgstr ""
"Jika Anda tidak memiliki pemindai kode batang, masukkan ke bidang nomor "
"pelacakan dan tekan <i>Enter</i> pada keyboard Anda"

#: includes/functions.php:8
msgid "Bulk Update"
msgstr "Pembaruan Massal"

#: includes/functions.php:29
