msgid "Close"
msgstr "Tutup"

#: templates/bulk-barcode.tpl.php:44
msgid "Update"
msgstr "Perbarui"

#: templates/single-barcode.tpl.php:43
msgid "Enter Shipment Number"
msgstr "Masukkan Nomor Pengiriman"

#: templates/single-barcode.tpl.php:55
msgid ""
"If you have connected your barcode scanner please scan directly to the "
"barcode and it will automatically update the Shipment Status"
msgstr ""
"Jika Anda telah menghubungkan pemindai kode batang Anda, silakan pindai "
"langsung ke kode batang dan secara otomatis akan memperbarui Status "
"Pengiriman"

#: templates/single-barcode.tpl.php:59
msgid ""
"If you don't have a barcode scanner please input the tracking number on the "
"field and press <i>Enter</i> on your keyboard"
msgstr ""
"Jika Anda tidak memiliki pemindai kode batang, masukkan nomor pelacakan di "
"bidang dan tekan <i>Enter</i> pada keyboard Anda"

#. Plugin Name of the plugin/theme
msgid "WPCargo Receiving Add-ons"
msgstr "WPCargo Receiving Add-ons"

#. Plugin URI of the plugin/theme
msgid "http://wpcargo.com/"
msgstr "http://wpcargo.com/"

#. Description of the plugin/theme
msgid ""
"This Add-ons will let you auto update the Shipment History by using the "
"barcode scanner or entering the number on the input fields."
msgstr ""
"Pengaya ini akan memungkinkan Anda memperbarui Riwayat Pengiriman secara "
"otomatis dengan menggunakan pemindai kode batang atau memasukkan nomor pada "
"bidang input."

